{
  "stem": "20142.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then one day, the entire group was sent to Majdanek in early 1942.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was about, in Pawiak about two months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I got out, I went to this working group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were allowed to return to ghetto, to their home, once a week.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were [INAUDIBLE] they-- they kept them all week long sleeping in the abnormal conditions, in dilapidated, bombed-out barracks of the former Polish-- Polish Army quarters.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on the weekend, they allowed the entire group to return together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I was wondering, is this-- is this, am I included?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I asked the foreman, he said to me, you silly fool.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You don't questions, you just do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how I got back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I got to ghetto, I-- then they want the [INAUDIBLE] that we had on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I contacted the people who could deliver the word through [INAUDIBLE] what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- he came to visit me very shortly and find out what's going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, we can't sacrifice anything of getting you out of there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let's see how that will work for another month.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But unfortunately, a month later, after I got for the first time-- after a long time not seeing [? mother, ?] there was [INAUDIBLE] in 1942, early even [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was sometime in April or end of April.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took us to Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There's an entire column of these people who were working, shipping coal to Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were came through Majdanek directly from on their trucks, with their coal, not expecting any tricks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they left us there for the-- a SS [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to take care of us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Drove away.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
